{"tid":431104,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"網民揭支那寶Android的app有嚴重私隱漏洞，每隔幾秒會偷拍照片","createTime":"2017-10-10T11:30:48.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-26T05:18:22.000Z","uid":3117,"like":94,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":33,"replies":[{"pid":"d7367d2587baf4fadd45b2fcc768ae57f1674486","tid":431104,"uid":3117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-10T11:30:48.000Z","msg":"網民揭app偷拍<br />\n<br />\n2016年2月中旬，有網民卻發現支付寶Android的app有嚴重私隱漏洞，不僅每隔幾秒會偷拍照片、錄音，還會將通訊錄、通話紀錄等個人資料上傳到伺服器。<br />\n<br />\n大陸用戶在Twitter中發文，稱支付寶Android版存在盜竊用戶隱私的情況。他表示支付寶app的偷拍過程很「高端」，會先開啟相機預覽、然後在預覽的畫面中選用一張，並非如一般照相般會會引發手機發出聲音。<br />\n<br />\n對於typcn的指控，支付寶官方微博就此回應稱，支付寶只申請業務需要的權限，不會做額外的信息採集和後台操作，更不會侵犯、洩露任何用戶隱私信息。<br />\n<br />\n有香港網民得悉後，並不感意外，有人留言：「大陸嘢一向都係咁，根本唔係新聞。唔咁做先係新聞囉。這不叫漏洞，叫惡意軟件。」亦有人奉勸：「所以千萬不能夠用支那人發明的apps.，大家小心。」"},{"pid":"db33957ad97a66db1a965e878d6fc38d4ad5ad13","tid":431104,"uid":29314,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-10T11:31:06.000Z","msg":"支那野"},{"pid":"9f9fa6bba7f0b6caf7b0f115e8f8439ca5127cf5","tid":431104,"uid":3117,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-10T11:32:02.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://evchk.wikia.com/wiki/支付寶\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fevchk.wikia.com%2Fwiki%2F%E6%94%AF%E4%BB%98%E5%AF%B6&d=g9ZhlBacktmsfUCJb49Fi10Hwm5JNK6yt%2FgZtp%2B4HOw%3D&h=0e87cd1c\" target=\"_blank\">http://evchk.wikia.com/wiki/支付寶</a>"},{"pid":"de2c1d7ed86f97aed6f582c5e5a3d4a11b42d9ca","tid":431104,"uid":3117,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-10T11:39:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"509ba4fae354c3b3f49a1d97dc741480681d1c7a","tid":431104,"uid":25845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-10T11:49:22.000Z","msg":"支那寶android app , 不了"},{"pid":"628400133460ba346b32d95d49c348f642650d7c","tid":431104,"uid":22675,"like":1,"dislike":8,"score":-7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-10T11:50:22.000Z","msg":"iphone版咪無問題囉"}